  <Hero
      title="Expert Repair for Your RollMover™ Compatible Equipment"
      tagline="Fast, Reliable Repair & Quality Parts for equipment compatible with RollMover™ RX, HD, XD, and LR series. Maximize uptime and save costs!"
      buttonText="Get a Free Quote"
      buttonUrl="#contact"
      disclaimerText="Artic Power Solutions is an independent service provider. RollMover™ is a trademark of Appleton Mfg. We are not affiliated with Appleton Mfg."
      imageUrl="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1727517786578-ff2bb896b852?q=80&w=2842&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.1.0&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D"
  />
  <main>

    <!-- Section 2: The Challenge -->
    <section
        id="challenge"
        class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white"
    >
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-md md:text-md font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Is Your Material Handling Equipment Performing at
          Its Best?</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-4">
          Heavy roll moving equipment is vital to your operations, but when it breaks down, it brings productivity to a
          halt.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Finding fast, reliable, and cost-effective repair service can be a challenge, especially when faced with
          warranty denials or providers who lack specialized knowledge.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section 3: Why Choose Us? -->
    <section
        id="why-us"
        class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-gray-50"
    >
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">The Artic Power Solutions Advantage</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-16 bg-yellow-100 border-l-4 border-yellow-500 p-8 rounded-r-lg shadow-lg max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <svg
                  class="h-16 w-16 text-yellow-600"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  aria-hidden="true"
              >
                <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
                />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800">Warranty Claim Denied? We Are Your Solution.</h3>
              <div class="mt-2 text-base text-gray-700">
                <p>Manufacturer warranties often have exclusions for "improper use," "unauthorized modifications," or
                  "normal wear and tear," leading to denied claims. <strong>If your repair isn't covered, you are not
                    out of options.</strong> We provide the fast, cost-effective repair solutions you need to get your
                  equipment running, regardless of its warranty status.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
          <ContentCard
              title="Specialized Expertise"
              description="We don't just fix equipment; we know roll moving systems inside and out. This is our focus, not a sideline."
          />
          <ContentCard
              title="Faster Turnaround"
              description="Our specialized focus means quicker diagnostics and repairs, minimizing your critical downtime."
          />
          <ContentCard
              title="Significant Cost Savings"
              description="Repair your equipment for a fraction of the cost of replacement, with transparent and fair pricing."
          />
          <ContentCard
              title="Nationwide Service"
              description="We serve clients nationwide, with a commitment to excellence and customer satisfaction."
          />


